 Review comment:
   using `_` in GTest names can lead to subtle collisions [and is specifically not recommended.](https://github.com/google/googletest/blob/master/googletest/docs/faq.md#why-should-test-suite-names-and-test-names-not-contain-underscore) You didn't introduce this but could you please fix this by removing that `_`? (If you rename `stl_allocator` to `allocator` then we won't have the problem)

